In fiction, a '''holocube''' is a small, futuristic object shaped like a [[cube]].  It is about the size of a [[Rubik's cube]], and can display short recorded video messages, in which a [[Holography|holographic]] object talks or demonstrates. It is featured as a key-item in the [[dystopian]] [[Video game|game]] [[Flashback: The Quest for Identity]]).

